    • entity中Account的使用

      entity中Account的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  CurrentAccount
      The current account class extends to account class(it can overdraft)
      class  JuniorAccount
      The junior account class extends to account class(only under 16 years old)
      class  SaverAccount
      The saver account class extends to account class(need to notice)

    • services中Account的使用

      参数类型为Account的services中的方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void Bank_Control.clearFunds(Account acc)
      This method is used to clear funds which are cheque.
      void Bank_Control.closeAccount(Account acc)
      This method is used to close a account.
      void Bank_Control.deposit(Account acc, int amount, boolean cleared)
      This method is used to deposit.
      void Bank_Control.giveNotice(Account acc, double amount)
      This method is used to give notice to withdraw(especially for saver account).
      void Bank_Control.reinstate(Account acc)
      This method is used to reinstate a account.
      void Bank_Control.suspend(Account acc)
      This method is used to suspend a account.
      void Bank_Control.withdraw(Account acc, int amount)
      This method is used to withdraw.
